# Workflow Defaults

When the user asks for new work, apply these defaults unless they explicitly say otherwise:

- Treat active work as homepage-first and new-route-first.
- Prefer implementing features on the main homepage (`app/page.tsx`) or in new routes such as `app/admire/page.tsx`.
- Ensure new routes are accessible from the main page navigation or links.
- Do not treat `/project` or any archive folder (including `(archive)` style folders) as primary working content.
- Use `/project` and archive content only when the user explicitly asks to work there.
